stichera_aposticha.text:
Today the Virgin gives birth to the Creator of all, * Paradise    offers a cave, and a star presents Christ as the Sun in darkness; 
    * the Magi with their gifts, enlightened by faith, adore; * 
    the shepherds behold a miracle, * while the angels exclaim:    Glory to God in the highest.

You were born of the Virgin in a cave; * the angels were    present and cried out: * Glory to You, O God, in the highest; * 
    for You were born from the womb of a Virgin and Mother ever-pure, 
    * in the form of a servant who renewed the world.

